{"word":"Jonah","slug":"jonah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jonah</b> <a href=\"#/H3124\">H3124</a> <br/> Called also Jonas.<br/> A prophet of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=25'>2Ki 14:25</a><br/> Sent by God to warn Nineveh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=1&verse=2'>Jon 1:2</a><br/> Disobedience and punishment of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=1&verse=17'>Jon 1:17</a><br/> Repentance and deliverance of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=2&verse=10'>Jon 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=40'>Mat 12:40</a><br/> Brought Ninevites to repentance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=3&verse=10'>Jon 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=41'>Mat 12:41</a><br/> Displeased with God's mercy to Nineveh; reproved<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=4&verse=11'>Jon 4:11</a><br/> Is a sign<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=4'>Mat 16:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=30'>Luk 11:30</a>"}]}